    \item Pomeron/Reggeon $t$-channel exchange dominates,
    \item Recoil particle is kinematically decoupled
    \end{itemize}
    \begin{itemize}
    \item Analysis at COMPASS
      \begin{itemize}
      \item Large data sample with high purity
