\section{COMPASS PWA}
\subsection{Data distributions}

\begin{frame}{$3\pi$ at COMPASS}{Kinematical distributions}
  \vspace{-2mm}
  \small
  \begin{itemize}
  \item The largest data set ($50\times 10^6$ events) on diffractively produced $3\pi$ systems.
  \item High-energy beam guaranties peripheral reaction $\sqrt{s} \approx 19\,$GeV.
  \item Many resonances are seen in the raw spectrum.
  \end{itemize}
