Model: a sum of $88^*$ partial waves
{\scriptsize
$$
A = c_1
\begin{pmatrix}
  \scalebox{0.45}{\cascadeUp{$1^{++}$}{$\rho$}}\\
  \scalebox{0.45}{\cascadeDn{$1^{++}$}{$\rho$}}\\
\end{pmatrix}
+c_2
\begin{pmatrix}
  \scalebox{0.45}{\cascadeUp{$2^{++}$}{$\rho$}}\\
  \scalebox{0.45}{\cascadeDn{$2^{++}$}{$\rho$}}\\
\end{pmatrix}
+c_3
\begin{pmatrix}
  \scalebox{0.45}{\cascadeUp{$2^{++}$}{$f_2$}}\\
  \scalebox{0.45}{\cascadeDn{$2^{++}$}{$f_2$}}\\
\end{pmatrix}
+\dots
$$
}
Likelihood Fit: a product of probability per event
{\scriptsize
$$
L = \prod_{e=1}^{{\color{red} \mathrm{Nevents}}} \frac{A(\tau_e)}{\int\mathrm{d}\tau_e A(\tau_e)},
\quad \tau = ({\color{blue!50!black}\sigma_1,\cos\theta_1,\phi_1,\cos\theta_{23},\phi_{23}})
$$
}
