        $$}
        \vspace{-5mm}
        \begin{itemize}
          \item Analytical continuation of $\rho(s)$:
          integral over the Dalitz plot for the complex energy
          \vspace{-2mm}
        {\scriptsize$$
        \hspace{-1cm}
        \rho(s) = \sum_\lambda\int \diff \Phi_3 \bigg| f_\rho(\sigma_1)d_{\lambda0}(\theta_{23}) - f_\rho(\sigma_3) d_{\lambda0}(\hat{\theta}_{3}+\theta_{12})\bigg|^2
        $$}
        \\\vspace{-3mm}
        \item Analytic contuation of $\rho$-meson decay amplitude $f_\rho$
        \scriptsize
          \begin{itemize}
            \item Breit-Wigner amplitude with the dynamic width
            \item $P$-wave Blatt-Weisskopf factors
