\section{Include Spin}
\begin{frame}{Partial-Wave Projection}
  Include spin via partial-wave projection:
  \begin{enumerate}
    \onslide<1->{\item Look at the partial wave for $a_1(1260)\to K\bar{K}\pi$ with isobar $K^*$}
    \onslide<2->{\item Project it onto the $3\pi$ final state with isobar $f_0(980)$}
    \onslide<3->{\item Obtain the first order approximation of the Khuri-Treiman approach}
