  \begin{block}{}
    \begin{itemize}
      \item $K\bar{K}\pi$ is a possible decay of the same resonance $a_1$
      \item Two separated problems? \pause No, more coupled states
      \item Hadron interaction mixes probabilities
    \end{itemize}
  \end{block}
