\begin{frame}{Data availability}
	Computed $\vec\alpha$ fields are available on \href{https://lc2pkpi-polarimetry.docs.cern.ch/}{our website} in JSON format over a 100x100 Dalitz plot grid.
    What we offer:
	\begin{itemize}
		\item the nominal model and all alternative models
		\item 100 parameter resamplings of the nominal model
	\end{itemize}
	This makes it possible to \textbf{propagate statistical and systematic uncertainties} in further analyses that use the $\varLambda_c^+\to p K^- \pi^+$ polarimetry field
\end{frame}

