\section{Introduction}

\begin{frame}{Motivation of the workshop}\
  \two\begin{columns}
    \begin{column}{0.57\textwidth}
      \begin{itemize}
        \item A lot of new heavy baryons are discovered
        \item Heavy baryons are narrow and well separated
        \item NR-approximation and spin symmetry give hits
        \item Interplay between QM states and M-B thresholds
        \item Many similarities between sectors
