\begin{frame}[noframenumbering]{Propagated uncertainties on the polarimeter field}
  \large
  We compute $\vec\alpha^{(i)}(\tau)$ over a phase space sample,
  with $i$ one of the parameter resamplings
  or one of the alterative amplitude models.\\[1.5em]
  Uncertainties are then visualized separately, using \\[1em]
