      \item {\color{red} new $T_{c\bar{s}}^a$} appear to be similar to $T_{cs}$ \\ % $\longleftrightarrow$
            \qquad HQSS is in action? Where is the good/bad diquark mass difference?\\[4mm]
      \item {\color{red} new $\chi_{c0} / T_{\psi\phi}$} close to the $D_s^+ D_s^-$ threshold.\\
            \qquad A hadronic molecule or the scalar charmonium?
            % \item new $T_{c\bar{s}}^a$ 
    \end{itemize}
  \end{alertblock}
\end{frame}

